text: Tatosoma is a genus of moths. It is part of the family Geometridae. Some of the species in this genus are: * Tatosoma alta - Philpott, 1913 * Tatosoma agrionata - Walker, 1862 * Tatosoma apicipallida - Prout, 1914 * Tatosoma lestevata - Philpott, 1914 * Tatosoma monoviridisata - Clarke, 1920 * Tatosoma tipulata - Walker, 1862 * Tatosoma topia - Philpott, 1903 ==References== *Natural History Museum Lepidoptera genus database Category:Geometridae
title: Tatosoma
